76
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:04,000
[SPEAKER_02] Meni je top, meni je baš dobro. Bogu hvala, ja sam...

77
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,000
[SPEAKER_02] Najsvježije.

78
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,000
[SPEAKER_02] Da, najsvježije možda to, ali...

79
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam najsvježiji čisto.

80
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, da.

81
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,000
[SPEAKER_02] Tebe sam ne pitao.

82
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,000
[SPEAKER_02] Niko ti nije pitao.

83
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,000
[SPEAKER_02] Niko mi nije pitao, istina.

84
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, meni je stvarno dobro, Bogu hvala i moja sinesoida je gore, iznad nule većinom.

85
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:29,000
[SPEAKER_02] Da, velikom, velikom većinom sam gore, tako da, baš je dobro. Meni je super.

86
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:33,000
