87
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih isto rekao da ova doljnja, kako se ona kaže...

88
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Amplituda.

89
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,000
[SPEAKER_02] Amplituda.

90
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,000
[SPEAKER_02] Amplituda, Igor.

91
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ide u neki minus, ajmo reći da je to samo nekakav...

92
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,000
